{"tid":1639104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[大家真係要入黎]撚狗唔係要屌","createTime":"2019-10-08T13:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T14:55:08.000Z","uid":216178,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"375700bc6f5726d80e3060413b3efd515c8736dc","tid":1639104,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:47:25.000Z","msg":"啱啱聽到金鐘有人屌狗就比人拉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以打呢篇文<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依家班狗</span></span>擺明大曬，佢有拘捕權又有炮，<span style=\"color: red;\">真係真係真係</span>唔可以硬碰，同佢理論真係冇可能（理性，有智慧嘅都唔會做狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) ，<span style=\"color: red;\">所以所以所以</span>對住班狗更加要忍，學杜生講，對住狗要扮有禮貌同尊重（班狗好受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撚狗大法</span></span>係要忍唔好屌，班狗最鐘意有人同佢吠，越嬲越過癮，用扮傻黎對應狗吠，例如傻笑，九唔搭八，千其唔好同佢有正常交流<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撚狗原則</span></span><br />\n好似玩123紅綠燈咁，佢喺度，我唔喐，佢唔喺度，我做乜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當佢見啲人有唔正常反應時，反而會思考下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阿蛇你越鐘意嘅，我就越唔做，咬我食呀啊蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">忠告 唔好太膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f23c8effb2f2c08b33a3372ae9988600940f4382","tid":1639104,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498faf88ad43dec5a1d4280db61bf25e8423a0f2","tid":1639104,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"忍住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94363b0b270aade8a07ba85fb8bd9c2321b37141","tid":1639104,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:53:32.000Z","msg":"唔好再屌 唔好再出聲<br />\n直接掉野 閃"},{"pid":"3bff956581220b864a00c6dbaa466fe2aa9d665d","tid":1639104,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:53:49.000Z","msg":"令狗認為笑  係恥笑緊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae824bfea91ede53020707d3c547003efc4cdd2","tid":1639104,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd115ce8f11d6a10a5ec11d741ae5729db1df46","tid":1639104,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"用手推"},{"pid":"7d218ca135943eb2d73f7c53c82b0816b9f54c61","tid":1639104,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:01:21.000Z","msg":"用腳推"},{"pid":"2afe348f1178dea8ddbd680734fc9aeae55b6d2d","tid":1639104,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:03:52.000Z","msg":"有冇人推"},{"pid":"cdbc24a0bbb6c5219919aa488467add697fef1ed","tid":1639104,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"冇人推"},{"pid":"d057938a687732f539313b014f79c57b5ef0